videos.description: Florida State's Derwin James plays perfect coverage and makes an athletic interception.
videos.headline: James gets up for interception

videos.description: James Blackman throws one deep to a wide open Nyqwan Murray for 51-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Blackman airs it out to Murray for 51-yard TD

videos.description: Cam Akers uses his breakaway speed to run it in from 54 yards out.
videos.headline: Akers rips off 54-yard TD run for Seminoles

videos.description: Eric Dungey finds Jamal Custis for an easy pitch-and-catch touchdown to cut the lead to 14-7.
videos.headline: Dungey hits wide open Custis for Syracuse TD

videos.description: Steve Ishmael comes down with a 34-yard touchdown grab to cut the deficit to 21-14.
videos.headline: Dungey hits Ishmael for leaping Syracuse TD

videos.description: D.J. Matthews drops the punt and Syracuse recovers to set themselves up in the red zone.
videos.headline: Florida State's Matthews muffs punt, Syracuse recovers

videos.headline: Dungey strolls in for Syracuse TD
